## 8. AI Relay Instructions

1. Read Core Philosophy entirely before acting.
2. Check Decision Log for binding constraints.
3. Update ONLY the JSON Machine-Readable State unless explicitly instructed.
4. When multiple contributors exist, respect parallel_synthesis mode.
5. Ask for human approval before moving to next session or phase.

